itHub (for code availability), ASCL (for code discovery), and a stated\nstrong preference from the new journal Astronomy & Computing for code release,\nwe expect to see additional progress over the next few years.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Dec 2012 20:25:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-11"}
